<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Campsite Approval Notification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 40px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; margin: auto; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #28a745; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        .logo { max-width: 150px; }
        .content { font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; padding: 20px 0; }
        .highlight { color: #28a745; font-weight: bold; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #28a745; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { font-size: 14px; color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="<%= companyLogo %>" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
            <h2 style="color: #28a745;">Campsite Approval Confirmation</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= providerName %>,</p>
            <p>We are pleased to inform you that your campsite, <strong>"<%= campsiteName %>"</strong>, has successfully passed our evaluation process and is now <span class="highlight">approved</span> for listing on our platform.</p>
            <p>Your commitment to providing a high-quality camping experience aligns with our values, and we look forward to a successful collaboration.</p>
            <p>You may now start receiving bookings and managing your campsite details directly from your dashboard.</p>
            <a href="https://yourplatform.com/dashboard" class="button">Access Your Dashboard</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= year %> BatoiBhai. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
